      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPEECHLESS (1) was well backed last start but ran below expectations when fifth (18.04), beaten 2 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Won at her only start from this draw. Can make amends. ASTON DEUTZ (8) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (23.41) at this track in a TG1-4W over 400m. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Likely to be in the finish again. KILCOY LASS (2) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish a nose away in second (17.90) at this track in a Grade 6 over 305m. Can measure up. GLIMMER OF HOPE (5) deserves plenty of thought over this trip.",
